title: If running `source` from within a script does not have the intended effect
pid: f6ed5c60-9229-4ae2-aec1-3bb9446d5e1c
body: |2-
  Try running the script by calling
    . ./script.sh
  rather than
    ./script.sh
  This makes its effects persist in the callilng shell.
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
